his way out of!

506
00:21:03,291 --> 00:21:05,250
He just stood there
like an idiot!

507
00:21:05,333 --> 00:21:08,958
[SHINJI cackling]
He's finished!

508
00:21:13,708 --> 00:21:15,041
What happened to me?

509
00:21:15,125 --> 00:21:16,708
What am I doing?

510
00:21:17,750 --> 00:21:18,666
[RITSU]
I'm going home.

511
00:21:18,750 --> 00:21:19,875
Huh?

512
00:21:19,958 --> 00:21:22,291
[RITSU] I don't actually
have psychic powers.

513
00:21:22,375 --> 00:21:23,541
--Oh, come on...
--[door slams]

514
00:21:23,625 --> 00:21:24,541
Hey!

515
00:21:24,625 --> 00:21:26,458
Kageyama, wait!

516
00:21:30,166 --> 00:21:31,166
[ARATAKA]
Hey...

517
00:21:32,708 --> 00:21:35,083
If it isn't Mob's
little brother.

518
00:21:36,208 --> 00:21:38,875
[ARATAKA] I see you're giving
me the cold shoulder, as usual.

519
00:21:38,958 --> 00:21:40,333
So what are you
wandering around

520
00:21:40,416 --> 00:21:41,916
near my house for?

521
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:43,083
It's for a job.

522
00:21:43,166 --> 00:21:45,333
I got a request to
exorcise a creepy ghost

523
00:21:45,416 --> 00:21:47,416
that's been showing
up in this area.

524
00:21:47,500 --> 00:21:48,750
Ya wanna help me out with it?

525
00:21:48,833 --> 00:21:50,250
Don't waste your breath.

526
00:21:50,333 --> 00:21:53,500
Unlike Shigeo, I don't have
any special psychic powers.

527
00:21:53,583 --> 00:21:55,083
Really, are you sure?

528
00:21:55,166 --> 00:21:58,125
I figured since Mob's your
older brother and all...

529
00:21:58,208 --> 00:21:59,625
[RITSU]
You figured wrong.

530
00:21:59,708 --> 00:22:01,500
Why don't you get rid
of that ghost yourself?

531
00:22:01,583 --> 00:22:03,041
Aren't you a psychic?

532
00:22:04,750 --> 00:22:07,083
He quit by throwing a
spoon instead of a towel?

533
00:22:07,166 --> 00:22:09,541
[laughs] He's got quite
the sense of humor,

534
00:22:09,625 --> 00:22:11,125
I'll give him that much.

535
00:22:11,208 --> 00:22:14,666
But, when it comes to talent,
he doesn't exactly seem blessed.

536
00:22:14,750 --> 00:22:17,291
Actually, you might be wrong.

537
00:22:17,375 --> 00:22:18,666
Take a look.

538
00:22:21,250 --> 00:22:23,583
[RITSU]
Hm? What's that?

539
00:22:25,791 --> 00:22:29,291
[RITSU]
It's not a balloon. What is it?

540
00:24:02,833 --> 00:24:04,000
[ARATAKA]
Ritsu continues to go wild

541
00:24:04,083 --> 00:24:05,291
by pairing up with Dimple.

542
00:24:05,375 --> 00:24:07,375
And then the gang leader
alliance makes its move.

543
00:24:07,458 --> 00:24:09,541
Meanwhile, some scary people
try to make Mob buy a vase.

544
00:24:09,625 --> 00:24:11,125
Both brothers are
in huge trouble!

